{
  "stem": "3804.3",
  "chunk_idx": 12,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "After we captured him, we knew that's good.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You know, we didn't know in the beginning.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But we got an information that is-- as I know, that it is, it was Fritz Bauer, the prosecutor of Hessen in Germany-- Jewish-- that he got a letter from a man called Hermann-- half Jew and half blind-- that his daughter is dating a man called Eichmann, a young man.",
      "word_count": 51
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Now it-- he heard it from [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the media through the radio that was the Nuremberg trial.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he heard suddenly that Eichmann is not there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he-- and it was Sicily.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I think his deputy of Eichmann was there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I said it's not my-- I'm not guilty, that my, my boss was Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So where is he?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Nobody knew where he is.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So I don't want to go back.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "Only if you ask me how it was escaped, that's another story.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "You want me to tell it now?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Sure, certainly.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So let's finish only that through the Nuremberg trial, when he heard it, Eichmann, he remembered that his boy is dating-- his girl is dating a man called Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 50,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He said, maybe his father is the, is the guy, is the man.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "He said yes.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'm going to teach him how to spell it.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he looked in his books.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "He didn't say Eckman.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, OK, go to the prison.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They took him prison.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And he dressed himself as an, as an aviator.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he ran away from prison.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then the Franciscan, the German church, furnished him with the, all the papers and send him to Argentina.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they had to do something with the American with the Eckman or Eichmann.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 51,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And then they helped him, the church.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
